1
00:01:37,860 --> 00:01:40,990
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,090 --> 00:01:43,990
[Episode 10]

3
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:48,200
Last time you asked me
to get two bottles of shampoo

4
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,640
from two different places.

5
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:51,240
What was the reason for that?

6
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:53,680
At this moment,

7
00:01:53,789 --> 00:01:55,650
I can't tell you too many details.

8
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:57,420
The whole story

9
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:59,840
hasn't been investigated thoroughly yet.

10
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,000
Then give me a sample.

11
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,660
I'll help you investigate it.

12
00:02:05,460 --> 00:02:07,380
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

13
00:02:39,370 --> 00:02:42,600
[Shampoo]

14
00:02:46,130 --> 00:02:47,630
[Shampoo]

15
00:02:50,380 --> 00:02:52,730
[Search for Similar Items]

16
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:55,420
[First-Tier Domestic Five-Star Hotel]

17
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:56,630
[Exclusive Shampoo for Purong,
100% Authentic, Click Here If You Know]

18
00:03:06,930 --> 00:03:08,960
Mr. Ji, the test results are out.

19
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:11,560
One of the bottles
is indeed a knockoff with fake labels.

20
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:14,020
There are plenty of these
in the underground wholesale markets.

21
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:15,020
Okay. Thank you.

22
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:23,790
[Purong Shampoo]

23
00:03:26,070 --> 00:03:26,810
[Essential Oil Formula
Hotel Toiletries Set]

24
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:27,620
[Deep Repair for a Healthy Glow]

25
00:03:27,660 --> 00:03:30,400
[First-Tier Domestic Five-Star Hotel,
Exclusive Shampoo for Purong]

26
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:41,200
[Dear, the minimum wholesale
order quantity is 50 items in this shop.]

27
00:03:41,230 --> 00:03:41,740
[I am offline now. Please add PR12445.]

28
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:42,360
[I'll reply once I see your messages.]

29
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:49,910
[PR12445] [Search]

30
00:03:52,990 --> 00:03:55,280
[Purong Authentic Products Porter]

31
00:03:57,870 --> 00:03:58,860
[Purong Authentic Products Porter]

32
00:03:59,110 --> 00:04:01,560
[Conditioner] [Shower Gel]

33
00:04:03,830 --> 00:04:05,070
[Purong]

34
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:09,650
[Shampoo]

35
00:04:12,270 --> 00:04:13,600
[Bad Review]

36
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:22,200
[Shampoo]

37
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:23,860
[Purong Authentic Products Porter]

38
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:41,130
Okay. My treat tonight.

39
00:04:41,150 --> 00:04:43,150
Let's not go home until we're drunk.

40
00:04:45,350 --> 00:04:45,500
[Favorites]

41
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:46,070
[Purong Authentic Products Porter]

42
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:48,580
[Send Message] [Audio/Video Call]

43
00:04:48,710 --> 00:04:50,250
[Shampoo]

44
00:04:54,330 --> 00:04:59,659
[Director's Office]

45
00:05:05,330 --> 00:05:06,390
What are you doing?

46
00:05:06,790 --> 00:05:07,850
What are you doing?

47
00:05:08,220 --> 00:05:09,160
I'm looking for my boss.

48
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,160
What are you doing?

49
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,510
I'm trying to stop you
from doing something stupid.

50
00:05:11,510 --> 00:05:13,120
I know what you've discovered.

51
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,560
But now is not the time to report it yet.

52
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,820
My time is running out.

53
00:05:15,870 --> 00:05:17,830
Now I have three bad reviews.

54
00:05:17,830 --> 00:05:19,980
Zhang Cailu
has already talked about firing me.

55
00:05:19,980 --> 00:05:21,010
Zhang Cailu?

56
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,730
That forewoman?

57
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:28,120
With this missing link adding to it,

58
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:30,250
the whole story makes much more sense.

59
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:33,230
Are you saying they are all in cahoots?

60
00:05:33,990 --> 00:05:35,350
I'm not sure yet.

61
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,680
However,

62
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:39,500
this industry chain
of reselling hotel supplies

63
00:05:39,500 --> 00:05:41,900
is too big for Zhang Cailu
to possess alone.

64
00:05:41,950 --> 00:05:43,830
She's just an underling at most.

65
00:05:44,810 --> 00:05:45,590
Things

66
00:05:46,070 --> 00:05:47,870
are not as simple as you thought.

67
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:51,780
In my opinion,
you're also not as simple as I thought.

68
00:05:51,780 --> 00:05:53,270
You left Svelto Hotel Group behind

69
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,830
and came all the way to Shanghai.

70
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:56,360
You've stayed here for so long

71
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:58,360
and meddled in so many things
that didn't concern you.

72
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,930
What's your purpose here exactly?

73
00:05:59,930 --> 00:06:01,600
You're definitely not here
for sightseeing.

74
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,970
You can't even protect yourself now.

75
00:06:02,970 --> 00:06:05,300
Yet you're still analyzing other people.

76
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:09,250
Now Zhang Cailu is in the open
while you are in the dark.

77
00:06:09,250 --> 00:06:10,830
You know
she's trying to find fault with you,

78
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:12,700
so just don't let her
get something on you anymore.

79
00:06:12,700 --> 00:06:13,220
Also,

80
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:15,230
try to avoid reporting issues by bypassing

81
00:06:15,230 --> 00:06:17,360
your immediate supervisor like this.

82
00:06:18,090 --> 00:06:19,530
Just do your job well.

83
00:06:22,310 --> 00:06:24,510
What does it have to do with you?

84
00:06:34,940 --> 00:06:35,680
Miyu.

85
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,720
I've been looking for you.

86
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:37,580
Looking for me?

87
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,460
Come with me to the Linen Room.

88
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:47,950
I'm fired?

89
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,270
Why?

90
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,820
I don't want you to leave, either.

91
00:06:50,820 --> 00:06:52,720
But the assessment results are here.

92
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:54,240
It can't be helped, Miyu.

93
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:56,920
You are indeed
not very suitable to work in our hotel.

94
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:57,720
Ms. Zhang,

95
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,160
you know how I got

96
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,160
these three bad reviews.

97
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,190
What's more, didn't you say

98
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:03,390
bad reviews would only affect bonuses?

99
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:05,240
The situation is different now.

100
00:07:05,260 --> 00:07:06,950
The competition in every industry
is so intense

101
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:08,600
that our hotel also has to

102
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:09,800
enhance the requirements for employees.

103
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,680
But

104
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:12,360
this does not comply
with the dismissal process

105
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,510
stated in the Hotel Staff Handbook.

106
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:15,150
I'm just notifying you in advance

107
00:07:15,150 --> 00:07:16,750
so that you can be mentally prepared.

108
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:18,190
The official notice will be issued soon.

109
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:19,000
Ms. Zhang,

110
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,260
the guest in Room 1801 is looking for you.

111
00:07:22,190 --> 00:07:23,000
Coming.

112
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:24,750
Let's leave it at that for now.

113
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:26,210
Just pack up and get ready.

114
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,630
Xu Miyu, you really can't go in.

115
00:07:31,630 --> 00:07:33,040
-I'll just talk to Mr. Wei for 2 minutes.
-You can't do this.

116
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,310
You need to make an appointment
to see Mr. Wei.

117
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:34,920
Mr. Wei.

118
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,240
I have some work-related matters

119
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,270
to report to you.

120
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:42,480
HSKP Department, Xu Miyu.

121
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,920
You guys go first. I'll be right there.

122
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,920
Okay, Mr. Wei.

123
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,860
Come in with me.

124
00:07:50,450 --> 00:07:52,740
[Shampoo]

125
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:53,000
The evidence you provided

126
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,050
probably does not constitute direct proof.

127
00:07:55,050 --> 00:07:55,440
Here.

128
00:07:56,130 --> 00:08:01,020
[Purong Hotel]

129
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:00,160
But as for the matters
you've reported to me,

130
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,360
I'm aware of them now.

131
00:08:01,390 --> 00:08:03,120
I will personally investigate this case.

132
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,580
No matter who is involved,

133
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,600
I will investigate it to the end

134
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,800
and show no leniency.

135
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:09,650
Can I apply to
participate in the investigation?

136
00:08:11,050 --> 00:08:12,600
I advise you not to get involved

137
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,510
in this matter.

138
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,700
The more people are involved,
the more complicated it'll get.

139
00:08:15,700 --> 00:08:16,600
If Zhang Cailu

140
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,900
and the people behind her
find out about this,

141
00:08:17,900 --> 00:08:19,850
it will not only be detrimental
to our subsequent investigation,

142
00:08:19,850 --> 00:08:21,120
but it might also bring you

143
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,160
some unnecessary trouble.

144
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:22,890
Understand?

145
00:08:24,130 --> 00:08:24,760
Okay.

146
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:27,040
Xu Miyu, right?

147
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,870
Thank you for telling me the information.

148
00:08:31,870 --> 00:08:33,789
As an employee of Purong Hotel,

149
00:08:33,820 --> 00:08:35,260
your sense of ownership

150
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,909
and sense of responsibility for the hotel

151
00:08:36,909 --> 00:08:38,150
have truly impressed me.

152
00:08:38,150 --> 00:08:38,880
Don't worry.

153
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,770
Leave this matter to me.

154
00:08:40,789 --> 00:08:42,150
Get back to work for now.

155
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:45,330
I'll definitely give you
a satisfactory answer.

156
00:08:46,550 --> 00:08:47,610
Thank you, Mr. Wei.

157
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:00,940
You don't need to come out.

158
00:09:01,190 --> 00:09:02,030
Xu Miyu.

159
00:09:02,390 --> 00:09:04,450
I am officially notifying you again.

160
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,720
You are fired.

161
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,720
Open your eyes and look carefully.

162
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:10,600
It has the director's signature

163
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,860
and the HR Department's official stamp.

164
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:14,350
Stop making trouble.

165
00:09:16,980 --> 00:09:18,490
[Employment Termination Notice]

166
00:09:18,510 --> 00:09:21,010
[Feng Kaixin,
Director of the Customer Department]

167
00:09:33,420 --> 00:09:34,270
Mr. Ji.

168
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,630
What happened?

169
00:09:38,740 --> 00:09:40,050
I'm leaving the hotel.

170
00:09:43,670 --> 00:09:44,790
So you reported it?

171
00:09:46,510 --> 00:09:48,820
Didn't I tell you
not to mess with Feng Kaixin?

172
00:09:48,820 --> 00:09:50,550
I didn't mess with Feng Kaixin.

173
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:54,660
Zhang Cailu suddenly said
I would be fired.

174
00:09:54,660 --> 00:09:56,080
I really had no other choices,

175
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,340
so I went to see Mr. Wei.

176
00:10:00,900 --> 00:10:02,640
Can I add you on WeChat?

177
00:10:02,660 --> 00:10:04,320
I still owe you 5,000 yuan.

178
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,720
When I gather enough money,

179
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,190
I'll transfer it to you on WeChat.

180
00:10:08,190 --> 00:10:10,000
We can talk about the money later.

181
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,260
Have you appealed yet?

182
00:10:11,860 --> 00:10:12,780
Yes, I have.

183
00:10:14,090 --> 00:10:15,620
Before the results are out,

184
00:10:16,070 --> 00:10:17,360
I won't leave.

185
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:20,800
But if...

186
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,870
my appeal gets no result,

187
00:10:25,750 --> 00:10:28,280
where can I find you
to return the money to you?

188
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:29,750
I'm right here.

189
00:10:30,260 --> 00:10:31,390
Will you always be here?

190
00:10:31,390 --> 00:10:32,520
I'll always be here.

191
00:10:53,640 --> 00:10:55,200
Why are you still coming here?

192
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,860
Take off your uniform at once,

193
00:10:56,870 --> 00:10:58,960
return it to the Uniform Room,
and wrap things up.

194
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,510
I still have a half-day shift to finish.

195
00:11:00,510 --> 00:11:01,750
Do you think you'll still get paid

196
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:03,000
for this half-day shift?

197
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,390
Whether I'll get paid or not,

198
00:11:04,390 --> 00:11:06,630
I'll finish the shift
which I'm supposed to finish.

199
00:11:06,630 --> 00:11:08,110
Ms. Zhang, the guest in Room 1812

200
00:11:08,110 --> 00:11:09,150
made a complaint.

201
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,120
Got it.

202
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:19,460
[Appeal Submitted, Pending Review]

203
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:31,990
[Appeal Submitted, Pending Review]

204
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:49,720
Miyu.

205
00:11:50,530 --> 00:11:51,890
Why don't you wait a bit longer?

206
00:11:51,890 --> 00:11:53,810
Black Card Ji
is making a complaint right now.

207
00:11:53,810 --> 00:11:55,630
It's driving Zhang Cailu crazy.

208
00:11:56,150 --> 00:11:58,410
Do you know what he's complaining about?

209
00:11:58,920 --> 00:11:59,830
The shampoo.

210
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:02,870
Is that so?

211
00:12:03,670 --> 00:12:05,520
Ke also once told me that

212
00:12:05,550 --> 00:12:08,000
Zhang Cailu targetting you
had something to do with the shampoo,

213
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,870
so don't be in a rush to leave now.

214
00:12:09,890 --> 00:12:10,890
Wait a bit longer.

215
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:12,160
There might be hope.

216
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:21,930
[HSKP Department, Xu Miyu]

217
00:12:27,350 --> 00:12:29,170
Complain... Let him complain.

218
00:12:30,070 --> 00:12:32,600
Just follow
the complaint handling process.

219
00:12:32,890 --> 00:12:34,510
Ask him to wait for us to handle it.

220
00:12:34,510 --> 00:12:35,510
I don't believe

221
00:12:35,510 --> 00:12:36,170
this matter

222
00:12:36,430 --> 00:12:37,750
won't cool down in three days.

223
00:12:37,750 --> 00:12:40,630
Mr. Feng, this complaint hit the bullseye.

224
00:12:41,010 --> 00:12:42,470
The guest has a black card,

225
00:12:42,470 --> 00:12:43,670
so he's very powerful.

226
00:12:43,670 --> 00:12:45,640
I'm afraid I'm no match for him.

227
00:12:45,670 --> 00:12:48,950
He's Ji Feng,
and I've had a drink with him before.

228
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,960
What's there to be afraid of?

229
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,960
Besides, no matter how powerful he is,

230
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,080
he's just a guest.

231
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:56,310
Is he going to stay at the hotel

232
00:12:56,340 --> 00:12:58,340
until the result comes out?

233
00:12:59,630 --> 00:13:00,960
Let me teach you a trick.

234
00:13:01,020 --> 00:13:02,270
If he is not satisfied,

235
00:13:02,270 --> 00:13:05,440
show him the list of fired employees.

236
00:13:05,650 --> 00:13:07,290
It's not that we didn't handle it.

237
00:13:07,290 --> 00:13:08,930
The rats have been caught.

238
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:11,020
Then we can withdraw the fakes

239
00:13:11,520 --> 00:13:12,680
and leave the issue aside for a few days.

240
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:14,880
This matter will blow over eventually.

241
00:13:15,170 --> 00:13:16,160
Yes.

242
00:13:16,230 --> 00:13:17,390
You're right.

243
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,930
Settle it quickly.

244
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:21,440
Can't you even solve such a small issue?

245
00:13:27,770 --> 00:13:28,810
[Aunt]

246
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:33,750
Wei Siyuan.

247
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:35,670
Aunt.

248
00:13:35,670 --> 00:13:38,600
Instead of
properly investigating the corruption,

249
00:13:38,750 --> 00:13:40,960
why did you fire an attendant?

250
00:13:41,510 --> 00:13:43,260
Being unable to solve the problem,

251
00:13:43,260 --> 00:13:45,720
you just dealt with the person
who raised it?

252
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:48,270
Is this how you manage Purong Hotel?

253
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:49,190
Well...

254
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:51,060
Aunt, which matter are you talking about?

255
00:13:51,060 --> 00:13:52,390
I've heard about the matter

256
00:13:52,390 --> 00:13:54,070
of the executive floor.

257
00:13:54,150 --> 00:13:56,080
Are you still playing dumb with me?

258
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:58,060
Aunt, please don't be angry.

259
00:13:58,090 --> 00:14:00,350
I really don't know anything about this.

260
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:01,960
I-I'll go investigate it thoroughly.

261
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:03,360
P-Please don't be angry.

262
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,390
Within today,

263
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:06,380
I want to see the investigation results.

264
00:14:06,380 --> 00:14:07,130
I'll be waiting.

265
00:14:07,130 --> 00:14:07,890
Okay.

266
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,100
Feng Kaixin.

267
00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:26,510
Can you use your brain when you do things?

268
00:14:26,510 --> 00:14:27,750
You even made a big mess

269
00:14:27,750 --> 00:14:29,360
of such a trivial matter.

270
00:14:30,680 --> 00:14:31,740
I'm sorry, Mr. Wei.

271
00:14:31,870 --> 00:14:33,270
What are you talking about?

272
00:14:33,270 --> 00:14:35,120
Besides that shady business
in your HSKP Department,

273
00:14:35,120 --> 00:14:36,510
what else could it be?

274
00:14:36,510 --> 00:14:37,870
I asked you to handle it carefully.

275
00:14:37,870 --> 00:14:40,240
I didn't tell you to fire her.

276
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:44,440
You mean Xu Miyu?

277
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:45,510
I don't care what her name is.

278
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:46,600
Let me tell you.

279
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:48,360
Old Madam is now blaming me.

280
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:49,270
What do you think I should do?

281
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:50,840
T-T-This is impossible.

282
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:52,720
I told the HR clerks to ask about it.

283
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:54,260
She has no background.

284
00:14:54,280 --> 00:14:56,000
How did she get connected
with the chairwoman?

285
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,000
Cut the crap.

286
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,270
Give me a solution right now.

287
00:14:58,270 --> 00:15:00,200
Otherwise, just pack up and leave!

288
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:02,660
What a useless man.

289
00:15:09,870 --> 00:15:11,520
Wu, find a resume for me.

290
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:13,750
She's from the executive floor
of the HSKP Department.

291
00:15:13,750 --> 00:15:14,510
Xu...

292
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:16,720
Xu Miyu.

293
00:15:16,880 --> 00:15:20,370
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

294
00:15:29,870 --> 00:15:31,360
According to the latest news,

295
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:33,550
the complaint from Black Card Ji
has escalated.

296
00:15:33,550 --> 00:15:35,270
Even the chairwoman heard about it.

297
00:15:35,270 --> 00:15:36,870
There will be a good show
to watch this time.

298
00:15:36,870 --> 00:15:37,750
Miyu!

299
00:15:39,510 --> 00:15:40,720
It's good that you haven't left.

300
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:43,150
Why didn't you tell me
about such a serious matter?

301
00:15:43,150 --> 00:15:44,750
It has nothing to do with you.

302
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:46,360
I don't want to drag you into this.

303
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:47,390
How would they dare?

304
00:15:47,390 --> 00:15:49,720
I would rip their skulls off
and make soup.

305
00:15:50,150 --> 00:15:50,720
Well...

306
00:15:51,020 --> 00:15:52,950
Are you planning to leave tonight?

307
00:15:53,150 --> 00:15:54,720
Stay at my place tonight.

308
00:15:54,740 --> 00:15:57,270
Tomorrow,
I'll go ask the HR clerks properly.

309
00:16:02,830 --> 00:16:03,830
[Notification:
Emergency Meeting for the Executive Floor]

310
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:03,840
What's wrong?

311
00:16:03,850 --> 00:16:04,670
[Everyone should go to the meeting room
for a meeting in 30 minutes.]

312
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:06,150
Emergency Meeting for the Executive Floor.

313
00:16:05,220 --> 00:16:05,870
[Feng Kaixin @ Xu Miyu]

314
00:16:06,870 --> 00:16:08,380
He even specifically tagged me.

315
00:16:08,380 --> 00:16:10,780
There's a sudden meeting
at this late hour?

316
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:13,360
Why are we having a meeting
so late at night?

317
00:16:19,180 --> 00:16:19,900
Mr. Feng.

318
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:21,750
Mr. Feng.

319
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:27,120
Is everyone here?

320
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:27,960
Yes.

321
00:16:28,660 --> 00:16:29,450
Okay.

322
00:16:30,270 --> 00:16:32,330
Since everyone is here, let's begin.

323
00:16:33,390 --> 00:16:36,000
I suddenly asked everyone
to have a meeting here tonight

324
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,120
because I'm going to announce

325
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:40,380
an important decision
for the hotel's personnel changes.

326
00:16:40,390 --> 00:16:43,750
As Zhang Cailu, the former forewoman
of the executive floor,

327
00:16:43,750 --> 00:16:45,880
violated work discipline seriously,

328
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:48,870
which affected Purong Hotel's image
in the industry

329
00:16:48,870 --> 00:16:50,270
and among its customers,

330
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:53,120
the hotel management
has unanimously decided

331
00:16:53,560 --> 00:16:55,750
to remove her from the position
of executive floor forewoman.

332
00:16:55,750 --> 00:16:56,630
Her dismissal

333
00:16:57,510 --> 00:16:58,670
is effective immediately.

334
00:16:58,670 --> 00:17:00,080
I'm fired?

335
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:01,120
Mr. Feng,

336
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:02,750
are you mistaken?

337
00:17:02,910 --> 00:17:05,970
This is a collective decision
by the hotel management.

338
00:17:07,760 --> 00:17:10,359
Do you think I'm making this up randomly?

339
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:13,730
Then tell me what rules I've broken.

340
00:17:13,819 --> 00:17:15,079
Haven't I been doing everything

341
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:17,540
according to the superiors' instructions?

342
00:17:17,670 --> 00:17:19,970
If you have any objection,
you can tell me after the meeting.

343
00:17:19,970 --> 00:17:21,880
But now I haven't finished speaking yet!

344
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:22,829
Sit down!

345
00:17:35,270 --> 00:17:36,270
Let's continue.

346
00:17:39,270 --> 00:17:40,000
Next,

347
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,880
I'm going to
announce a personnel appointment.

348
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:44,110
From today onwards,

349
00:17:44,510 --> 00:17:46,570
the forewoman of the executive floor

350
00:17:46,850 --> 00:17:48,310
will be taken up by Xu Miyu.

351
00:17:52,020 --> 00:17:53,480
Congratulations, Ms. Xu.

352
00:18:02,350 --> 00:18:03,110
I hope

353
00:18:03,510 --> 00:18:06,840
from now on, you can lead everyone
to make progress together

354
00:18:07,110 --> 00:18:09,940
and improve the executive floor's work
to a higher level.

355
00:18:09,940 --> 00:18:10,450
Come on.

356
00:18:10,620 --> 00:18:12,560
Let's all give Ms. Xu

357
00:18:12,720 --> 00:18:14,960
a round of applause and cheer her on.

358
00:18:36,950 --> 00:18:37,880
-Mr. Ji.
-Hello.

359
00:18:38,510 --> 00:18:39,440
I'm Feng Kaixin.

360
00:18:39,610 --> 00:18:40,140
Mr. Feng.

361
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:42,890
Our department
has just finished a meeting.

362
00:18:42,890 --> 00:18:45,680
Regarding the shampoo quality issue
you raised,

363
00:18:45,710 --> 00:18:46,800
we've punished

364
00:18:46,820 --> 00:18:48,610
the relevant personnel severely.

365
00:18:48,610 --> 00:18:49,610
Who was punished?

366
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:50,720
Zhang Cailu,

367
00:18:51,010 --> 00:18:52,550
the forewoman of the executive floor.

368
00:18:52,550 --> 00:18:53,720
She has been fired.

369
00:18:54,470 --> 00:18:55,890
Sorry for the trouble, Mr. Feng.

370
00:18:55,890 --> 00:18:57,160
Please don't say that.

371
00:18:57,180 --> 00:19:00,360
Mr. Ji, you have a sharp eye.

372
00:19:00,380 --> 00:19:02,510
You helped our hotel get rid of a pest.

373
00:19:02,540 --> 00:19:04,370
We should be thanking you.

374
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:07,680
To express our apologies,

375
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:09,440
we've specially prepared this

376
00:19:09,460 --> 00:19:11,790
hotel toiletries gift box.

377
00:19:11,810 --> 00:19:14,270
It's just a small token
of our appreciation.

378
00:19:14,710 --> 00:19:16,320
Thank you. It's my honor.

379
00:19:16,610 --> 00:19:17,800
I won't disturb you any longer.

380
00:19:17,800 --> 00:19:19,400
Call me if you need anything.

381
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:20,090
Thank you.

382
00:19:31,440 --> 00:19:32,170
Come in.

383
00:19:37,030 --> 00:19:37,720
Mr. Wei.

384
00:19:38,190 --> 00:19:39,820
Mr. Feng has promoted

385
00:19:39,850 --> 00:19:41,510
Xu Miyu to forewoman as you requested.

386
00:19:41,510 --> 00:19:43,030
The situation
with the former executive floor forewoman

387
00:19:43,030 --> 00:19:44,720
has also been handled properly.

388
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:46,820
Tell him to keep a low profile these days.

389
00:19:46,820 --> 00:19:47,410
Okay.

390
00:19:50,310 --> 00:19:52,840
There's one more thing
I need to report to you.

391
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:53,880
Go ahead.

392
00:19:54,070 --> 00:19:56,510
Mr. Ji Feng,
who you asked me to investigate last time,

393
00:19:56,510 --> 00:19:58,370
is a black card guest in our hotel.

394
00:19:58,720 --> 00:19:59,920
As for the executive floor incident
this time,

395
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:03,650
he was the guest who used
black card privileges to make a complaint.

396
00:20:06,270 --> 00:20:07,400
Did he meet with the chairwoman?

397
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:08,310
No, he didn't.

398
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,780
But I've checked his background.

399
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:12,960
Since he graduated
from Birmingham three years ago,

400
00:20:12,960 --> 00:20:15,510
he's been moving across
various countries and regions,

401
00:20:15,510 --> 00:20:18,910
working as a professional manager
to launch hotel business.

402
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:21,360
Previously,
a rumor came out from the board,

403
00:20:21,360 --> 00:20:22,640
saying that they would
find a professional manager

404
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:24,270
to take over the hotel management.

405
00:20:24,270 --> 00:20:26,000
At this time, he appeared at...

406
00:20:34,490 --> 00:20:37,100
[Wei Siyuan, In His Youth]

407
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:40,160
Okay. I got it.

408
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:46,130
You're quite smug, aren't you?

409
00:20:50,150 --> 00:20:52,790
Mr. Wei, what are you talking about?

410
00:21:00,970 --> 00:21:03,300
On what grounds could you steal my things?

411
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:08,610
Keep a close eye on him for me.

412
00:21:08,610 --> 00:21:10,500
Report to me if anything happens.

413
00:21:10,750 --> 00:21:11,240
Okay.

414
00:21:11,310 --> 00:21:17,500
[Purong Hotel]

415
00:21:25,750 --> 00:21:26,960
What did I tell you?

416
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:30,060
Making a comeback
is the main theme of your life.

417
00:21:30,200 --> 00:21:30,890
Cheers.

418
00:21:31,820 --> 00:21:32,410
Cheers.

419
00:21:35,630 --> 00:21:37,540
I still feel like I'm dreaming.

420
00:21:37,570 --> 00:21:40,030
In the morning,
they said they would fire me.

421
00:21:40,070 --> 00:21:41,270
But in the evening, inexplicably,

422
00:21:41,270 --> 00:21:42,700
they said
they would promote me to forewoman.

423
00:21:42,700 --> 00:21:44,750
Maybe that Black Card Ji's complaint

424
00:21:44,750 --> 00:21:46,000
really worked.

425
00:21:46,810 --> 00:21:48,340
You've met your lucky star.

426
00:21:48,690 --> 00:21:50,930
Can you go to any room

427
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:52,220
on the executive floor

428
00:21:52,220 --> 00:21:54,440
and bring me a bottle of shampoo
from there?

429
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:55,850
Can you guarantee

430
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:57,510
this matter won't affect

431
00:21:57,510 --> 00:21:59,020
the hotel's normal services?

432
00:21:59,020 --> 00:22:00,430
Okay. Just rest assured.

433
00:22:01,270 --> 00:22:03,030
He's not my lucky star.

434
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,880
He's the instigator.

435
00:22:05,890 --> 00:22:08,150
It sounds like there's a story behind it.

436
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:10,000
Regarding this shampoo incident
I've told you,

437
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:11,270
he was the one investigating it.

438
00:22:11,270 --> 00:22:13,270
I was just a scapegoat.

439
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:16,730
Then your current situation

440
00:22:16,780 --> 00:22:18,380
is very easy to understand.

441
00:22:19,890 --> 00:22:21,720
Do you know that Black Card Ji?

442
00:22:21,800 --> 00:22:23,750
I've heard of him,
but I couldn't match the name to the face.

443
00:22:23,750 --> 00:22:25,030
It wasn't until last time,

444
00:22:25,030 --> 00:22:26,720
at Mr. Duan Jr.'s caviar banquet,

445
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:28,030
that I saw him for the first time.

446
00:22:28,030 --> 00:22:30,680
He has always had a good reputation
in the industry.

447
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:32,360
Nor has he had any dark history.

448
00:22:32,360 --> 00:22:33,920
If you want to learn about him,

449
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:35,320
you can check his resume.

450
00:22:35,530 --> 00:22:37,530
I don't have time to learn about him.

451
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:39,460
But lately, I've been thinking

452
00:22:39,460 --> 00:22:42,350
though some people seemed annoying to you,

453
00:22:42,750 --> 00:22:45,510
then they just saved you by chance.

454
00:22:45,720 --> 00:22:47,960
Some people seemed nice to you,

455
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:49,810
but then they suddenly turned against you,

456
00:22:49,810 --> 00:22:51,010
becoming hypocrites

457
00:22:51,270 --> 00:22:53,590
and stabbing you in the back
while you were unaware of it.

458
00:22:53,590 --> 00:22:56,450
Now you know how dangerous
the workplace is, right?

459
00:22:57,240 --> 00:22:58,240
Let me tell you.

460
00:22:58,310 --> 00:23:00,680
Those guests on your executive floor

461
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:01,920
are full of hidden talents.

462
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:03,570
There are all kinds of people there.

463
00:23:03,570 --> 00:23:05,130
When some of them speak,

464
00:23:05,400 --> 00:23:07,660
even Wei Siyuan doesn't dare to disobey.

465
00:23:09,030 --> 00:23:10,920
Even if Black Card Ji had saved me,

466
00:23:11,550 --> 00:23:12,640
why do you think

467
00:23:12,640 --> 00:23:15,030
Mr. Feng promoted me to forewoman?

468
00:23:15,750 --> 00:23:18,140
In terms of seniority and ability,

469
00:23:18,370 --> 00:23:20,940
or youth and strength,
I'm not even qualified.

470
00:23:20,940 --> 00:23:22,960
Forewoman
isn't a very high-ranking position.

471
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:25,410
We don't know yet
whether it's something good or bad.

472
00:23:25,410 --> 00:23:27,240
Let me
highlight the main points for you now.

473
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:28,960
Xu Miyu, remember this.

474
00:23:29,070 --> 00:23:31,030
Not only are the guests
on your executive floor

475
00:23:31,030 --> 00:23:33,070
all quite influential,

476
00:23:33,130 --> 00:23:35,720
but your colleagues
are also not to be trifled with.

477
00:23:35,720 --> 00:23:37,510
Even though they might look young,

478
00:23:37,510 --> 00:23:39,680
their workplace experience

479
00:23:39,680 --> 00:23:41,240
is definitely more extensive than yours.

480
00:23:41,240 --> 00:23:43,240
I advise you to be mentally prepared.

481
00:23:43,240 --> 00:23:45,180
It won't be easy for you

482
00:23:45,330 --> 00:23:46,570
to make them respect you.

483
00:23:46,570 --> 00:23:48,980
I know it's not easy
to be their forewoman.

484
00:23:49,270 --> 00:23:51,790
But this is just the beginning.

485
00:23:52,030 --> 00:23:53,960
From now on, I'm going to

486
00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:56,720
learn how to use a manager's mindset
and perspective

487
00:23:56,720 --> 00:23:58,510
to look at the executive floor,

488
00:23:58,510 --> 00:23:59,510
the HSKP Department

489
00:23:59,510 --> 00:24:01,240
and even the entire Purong Hotel.

490
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:03,680
I'd like to see
how far I can go in this place.

491
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:06,680
Right! This is the Xu Miyu I know.

492
00:24:06,750 --> 00:24:08,510
Dealing with whatever happens to you

493
00:24:08,510 --> 00:24:10,110
and never taking a step back.

494
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:12,310
I still remember when you were a kid,

495
00:24:12,310 --> 00:24:15,070
even though your stepfather
and mother treated you like that,

496
00:24:15,070 --> 00:24:17,000
I never saw you cry.

497
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:19,510
And you always did things
better than your sister.

498
00:24:19,510 --> 00:24:21,790
I think since childhood, you've been

499
00:24:21,790 --> 00:24:24,320
a strong heroine
who can always turn the tide.

500
00:24:25,510 --> 00:24:25,970
Come on.

501
00:24:26,120 --> 00:24:28,390
Let's drink to your workplace debut.

502
00:24:36,440 --> 00:24:37,430
I'm back.

503
00:24:42,410 --> 00:24:43,300
Ke Wenxue.

504
00:24:43,960 --> 00:24:44,880
Why don't you ask about it?

505
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:46,070
She's back now.

506
00:24:46,640 --> 00:24:47,640
Ask her directly.

507
00:24:47,640 --> 00:24:49,640
On what grounds
can she become the forewoman?

508
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:50,970
I'd like to hear it, too.

509
00:24:58,720 --> 00:24:59,680
Ms. Xu.

510
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:00,880
Qingping.

511
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:02,200
Don't try to cozy up to me.

512
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:03,880
If you have the guts,
tell everyone the truth.

513
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:05,740
How did you become the forewoman?

514
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:10,310
I was also very surprised
to hear this news.

515
00:25:10,310 --> 00:25:11,490
You're still pretending, huh?

516
00:25:11,490 --> 00:25:13,200
When Black Card Ji
cancelled your bad reviews,

517
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:14,160
I could sense it.

518
00:25:14,160 --> 00:25:15,920
You have such a strong background.

519
00:25:15,920 --> 00:25:17,160
Since you have such a powerful backer,

520
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:19,100
why are you here
to compete with us for the forewoman?

521
00:25:19,100 --> 00:25:20,350
You should go to the board and tell them

522
00:25:20,350 --> 00:25:21,510
to directly appoint you as the director.

523
00:25:21,510 --> 00:25:22,720
Isn't that even more awesome?

524
00:25:22,720 --> 00:25:23,680
Just like everyone else,

525
00:25:23,680 --> 00:25:25,160
I was hired by the hotel
through an interview.

526
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:26,550
I don't have any backers.

527
00:25:26,550 --> 00:25:28,960
But since the hotel
has promoted me to forewoman,

528
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:30,220
there must be a reason.

529
00:25:31,880 --> 00:25:34,080
Because of your three bad reviews, huh?

530
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:35,680
Then I really couldn't catch up
in my whole life

531
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:37,010
no matter how hard I try.

532
00:25:59,240 --> 00:26:00,030
Yin Xiang.

533
00:26:01,130 --> 00:26:02,170
Miyu.

534
00:26:03,270 --> 00:26:04,200
You look great

535
00:26:04,700 --> 00:26:07,630
in this outfit.

536
00:26:08,880 --> 00:26:10,270
Do you also think I...

537
00:26:10,270 --> 00:26:11,110
No, I don't.

538
00:26:11,590 --> 00:26:13,520
It's good to become the forewoman.

539
00:26:14,030 --> 00:26:16,990
Luo Qingping is unhappy

540
00:26:17,110 --> 00:26:20,040
because she thought
she could become the forewoman.

541
00:26:26,240 --> 00:26:28,030
It's fine. She's just like that.

542
00:26:28,030 --> 00:26:28,960
Just ignore her.

543
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:16,720
Thank you all for coming to work on time.

544
00:27:20,790 --> 00:27:22,650
You're even thanking us for that?

545
00:27:23,110 --> 00:27:25,590
Then if I clean
more than a dozen rooms every day,

546
00:27:25,590 --> 00:27:28,590
you might even
have to give me an honorary banner, huh?

547
00:27:31,510 --> 00:27:33,570
Today's morning meeting is about...

548
00:27:33,680 --> 00:27:36,920
Then I'll sue them
for violating the Labor Contract Law!

549
00:27:37,680 --> 00:27:38,640
They notified me in the morning

550
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:40,160
and asked me to leave in the afternoon.

551
00:27:40,160 --> 00:27:41,960
They didn't give me
a one-month notice in advance.

552
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:44,400
Nor did they pay me double
for the last month.

553
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:46,030
Mr. Lin, you are so lucky.

554
00:27:46,030 --> 00:27:47,680
The last sunlit guest room
on the executive floor

555
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:49,010
just became available.

556
00:27:49,110 --> 00:27:51,160
Room 1812. It's all set.

557
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:51,200
[Purong Hotel] [Resident Identity Card
of the People's Republic of China]

558
00:27:51,160 --> 00:27:52,550
The elevator is over there.

559
00:27:52,550 --> 00:27:54,030
I've worked in the company
for over 10 years.

560
00:27:54,030 --> 00:27:56,040
Can they just fire me so suddenly?

561
00:27:56,830 --> 00:27:58,890
How could they deal with it like this?

562
00:28:04,750 --> 00:28:07,580
[Weekly Shift Schedule
for Executive Floor Staff]

563
00:28:04,830 --> 00:28:06,790
Have you all
seen this week's shift schedule?

564
00:28:06,790 --> 00:28:07,660
Do you have any suggestions?

565
00:28:07,660 --> 00:28:09,510
A shift schedule is arranged so complexly.

566
00:28:09,510 --> 00:28:10,350
Just some superficial efforts.

567
00:28:10,350 --> 00:28:11,070
Exactly.

568
00:28:12,400 --> 00:28:13,160
Ms. Xu.

569
00:28:13,690 --> 00:28:14,410
Go ahead.

570
00:28:14,730 --> 00:28:16,260
I need to go to the restroom.

571
00:28:16,350 --> 00:28:17,160
Just go.

572
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:23,680
Ke.

573
00:28:24,710 --> 00:28:25,770
Your mobile phone.

574
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:27,310
Ms. Xu, someone made a complaint.

575
00:28:27,310 --> 00:28:28,110
I need to go deal with it.

576
00:28:28,110 --> 00:28:29,310
Go. Just go now.

577
00:28:31,750 --> 00:28:33,520
This regular meeting is held
in quite a democratic way.

578
00:28:33,520 --> 00:28:34,930
Isn't it a waste of time?

579
00:28:36,790 --> 00:28:37,590
Ms. Xu.

580
00:28:38,140 --> 00:28:40,270
I want to apply for five days
of compensatory leave

581
00:28:40,270 --> 00:28:41,270
to prepare for the exam.

582
00:28:41,270 --> 00:28:42,110
Five days?

583
00:28:42,790 --> 00:28:44,240
Isn't that too long?

584
00:28:44,550 --> 00:28:47,880
Previously, we only
had three consecutive days off at most.

585
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:50,310
That's because
you haven't been here long enough, Ms. Xu.

586
00:28:50,310 --> 00:28:52,030
When Ms. Zhang was here,

587
00:28:52,350 --> 00:28:54,480
we could take more than three days off.

588
00:28:56,350 --> 00:28:58,510
Then I'll go back
and check your leave record.

589
00:28:58,510 --> 00:28:59,110
No need.

590
00:28:59,220 --> 00:29:00,640
Over the past three years,
I've accumulated

591
00:29:00,640 --> 00:29:01,550
27 days of compensatory leave,

592
00:29:01,550 --> 00:29:02,920
not even including
this year's annual leave.

593
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:04,160
Not to mention taking five days off,

594
00:29:04,160 --> 00:29:05,820
I can even take five weeks off.

595
00:29:06,550 --> 00:29:08,290
Then when will you start your leave?

596
00:29:08,290 --> 00:29:09,180
Today.

597
00:29:11,110 --> 00:29:12,070
Today?

598
00:29:13,070 --> 00:29:14,750
There's a conference in our hotel now.

599
00:29:14,750 --> 00:29:16,310
The executive floor is fully booked.

600
00:29:16,310 --> 00:29:17,510
We are short-handed.

601
00:29:17,550 --> 00:29:18,960
Does that have anything to do with me?

602
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:20,000
As a leader,

603
00:29:20,110 --> 00:29:21,310
you should have considered in advance

604
00:29:21,310 --> 00:29:22,750
the issue
of employees taking compensatory leave.

605
00:29:22,750 --> 00:29:24,950
Bargaining with your subordinates now

606
00:29:25,240 --> 00:29:26,440
shows no competence.

607
00:29:27,270 --> 00:29:29,510
I've rejected your application
of compensatory leave.

608
00:29:29,510 --> 00:29:31,310
Tell your parents to come next month.

609
00:29:31,310 --> 00:29:34,510
Drop everything this month
no matter how important it is.

610
00:29:36,430 --> 00:29:36,960
Alright.

611
00:29:37,430 --> 00:29:39,160
Then you can take five days off.

612
00:29:42,750 --> 00:29:44,240
Ms. Xu, I want to take a leave, too.

613
00:29:44,240 --> 00:29:45,640
If other employees want to take a leave,

614
00:29:45,640 --> 00:29:47,250
wait until Luo Qingping comes back.

615
00:29:47,250 --> 00:29:49,350
Why can she take a leave but I can't?

616
00:29:49,350 --> 00:29:51,240
She's preparing
for the Adult College Entrance Exam

617
00:29:51,240 --> 00:29:52,700
to change her own destiny.

618
00:29:52,820 --> 00:29:54,880
Does taking a stupid exam
make her superior?

619
00:29:54,880 --> 00:29:56,150
You just heard it, too.

620
00:29:56,510 --> 00:29:59,160
Luo Qingping has accumulated 27 days
of compensatory leave these three years,

621
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:00,510
which means she has been working

622
00:30:00,510 --> 00:30:02,240
without any days off all year round,

623
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:04,240
so it's reasonable for her
to take this leave.

624
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:06,960
Gosh. What a double standard.

625
00:30:15,590 --> 00:30:17,750
Our hotel's employee handbook says

626
00:30:17,750 --> 00:30:20,350
two people on the same floor
can't take a leave at the same time,

627
00:30:20,350 --> 00:30:22,790
so I'm not making things difficult
for you all on purpose.

628
00:30:22,790 --> 00:30:24,750
Guys, please understand.

629
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:26,430
Mi-

630
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:28,340
Ms. Xu, come here quickly.

631
00:30:30,010 --> 00:30:30,930
Coming.

632
00:30:31,790 --> 00:30:33,320
That's all for the meeting.

633
00:30:33,830 --> 00:30:34,790
Miyu.

634
00:30:36,290 --> 00:30:37,050
Miyu.

635
00:30:37,950 --> 00:30:38,830
Go ahead.

636
00:30:40,030 --> 00:30:42,750
I'm sorry, Mr. Lin. I'm sorry.

637
00:30:42,750 --> 00:30:44,390
Are you playing tricks on me?

638
00:30:44,550 --> 00:30:46,210
The receptionist just told me

639
00:30:46,350 --> 00:30:48,410
there was only this sunlit room left.

640
00:30:48,550 --> 00:30:49,950
And now you're telling me

641
00:30:50,550 --> 00:30:52,280
to move to another sunlit room.

642
00:30:52,400 --> 00:30:53,480
How did you magically produce

643
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:54,960
so many sunlit rooms?

644
00:30:55,110 --> 00:30:56,000
Was the receptionist lying to me

645
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:57,030
or are you?

646
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:58,750
Do I look gullible?

647
00:31:01,000 --> 00:31:02,670
I'm sorry, Mr. Lin.

648
00:31:03,310 --> 00:31:04,510
Please calm down.

649
00:31:04,550 --> 00:31:05,550
I can't calm down.

650
00:31:05,750 --> 00:31:07,680
Why isn't your forewoman here yet?

651
00:31:08,350 --> 00:31:09,510
I'll rush her.

652
00:31:12,550 --> 00:31:13,270
Yin Xiang.

653
00:31:13,550 --> 00:31:16,610
I will take your menstrual cramps
into consideration.

654
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:17,790
How about this?

655
00:31:17,790 --> 00:31:19,920
I'll cover Luo Qingping's shift tonight.

656
00:31:19,920 --> 00:31:20,500
Really?

657
00:31:20,790 --> 00:31:21,790
Thank you, Miyu.

658
00:31:22,270 --> 00:31:24,450
Ms. Xu, where are you?

659
00:31:25,350 --> 00:31:26,000
Coming.

660
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:27,000
Which room is it?

661
00:31:29,160 --> 00:31:31,110
You're lucky now.

662
00:31:31,110 --> 00:31:32,670
Someone's got your back.

663
00:31:33,640 --> 00:31:34,640
Speaking of Miyu,

664
00:31:34,750 --> 00:31:36,210
she's very easy to talk to.

665
00:31:46,560 --> 00:31:47,430
Ji...

666
00:31:50,110 --> 00:31:51,070
Mr. Ji.

667
00:31:51,160 --> 00:31:52,270
What are you doing here?

668
00:31:52,270 --> 00:31:54,270
Ask your forewoman to come here now.

669
00:31:54,350 --> 00:31:56,880
I'm the new forewoman
of the executive floor.

670
00:31:57,070 --> 00:31:58,510
You are the forewoman?

671
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:07,690
What's going on?

672
00:32:07,750 --> 00:32:09,010
It's a double booking.

673
00:32:26,070 --> 00:32:27,350
Mr. Lin, right?

674
00:32:27,350 --> 00:32:28,640
I'm the forewoman of the executive floor.

675
00:32:28,640 --> 00:32:29,790
My name is Xu Miyu.

676
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:33,790
Here's the thing.

677
00:32:33,790 --> 00:32:35,270
T-Today, our...

678
00:32:35,270 --> 00:32:36,750
Your computer is broken.

679
00:32:36,840 --> 00:32:38,840
She has said it eight times already.

680
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:40,000
Do you think

681
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:42,070
it's okay
if I arrange another room for you?

682
00:32:42,070 --> 00:32:43,240
It's not okay!

683
00:32:43,550 --> 00:32:44,880
Why should I give in?

684
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:46,750
I gave in and then lost my job!

685
00:32:46,750 --> 00:32:48,790
Why do you still want me to give in?

686
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:51,160
I've agreed
to transfer to another department.

687
00:32:51,160 --> 00:32:53,590
Why do they still insist on laying me off?

688
00:32:53,590 --> 00:32:56,270
Why am I always the one getting hurt?

689
00:32:56,270 --> 00:32:57,790
Am I just unlucky?

690
00:32:59,000 --> 00:33:00,790
I can understand how you feel.

691
00:33:01,440 --> 00:33:02,700
But here's the thing.

692
00:33:03,220 --> 00:33:04,830
This room has always been occupied

693
00:33:04,830 --> 00:33:06,000
by Mr. Ji,

694
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:07,750
so I think for the sake of convenience...

695
00:33:07,750 --> 00:33:09,510
-Maybe it's still...
- What convenience?

696
00:33:09,510 --> 00:33:12,000
So "first come, first served"
also applies in checking into hotels, huh?

697
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:14,350
Do I need to show you my resume?

698
00:33:14,350 --> 00:33:16,830
They said the ones who came first
surpassed me in seniority.

699
00:33:16,830 --> 00:33:18,830
And they said the ones who came later
were young and strong,

700
00:33:18,830 --> 00:33:20,590
being easier to order around than me.

701
00:33:20,590 --> 00:33:21,750
Let me tell you!

702
00:33:21,750 --> 00:33:23,350
I'm just staying here today!

703
00:33:23,510 --> 00:33:24,550
I just want this sunshine

704
00:33:24,550 --> 00:33:25,920
and this view!

705
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:27,590
I've worked day and night
for over 10 years!

706
00:33:27,590 --> 00:33:30,310
I'm just going to enjoy my life properly!

707
00:33:32,550 --> 00:33:33,480
I'm just going to enjoy my life properly.

708
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:34,200
Mr. Ji.

709
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:35,440
I won't give in to anyone.

710
00:33:35,440 --> 00:33:36,310
From now on,

711
00:33:36,310 --> 00:33:37,200
I'll do whatever I want.

712
00:33:37,200 --> 00:33:38,440
Clean the room at once.

713
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:40,350
Mr. Lin, welcome to our hotel.

714
00:33:40,370 --> 00:33:42,070
I'd like to apologize to you again.

715
00:33:42,070 --> 00:33:42,790
Mr. Ji.

716
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:46,610
Mr. Ji, let me do it.

717
00:33:48,590 --> 00:33:51,350
I also want to thank you
for helping me keep my job.

718
00:33:54,510 --> 00:33:57,510
Your promotion to forewoman
has nothing to do with me.

719
00:33:58,130 --> 00:33:59,690
I also don't know what happened,

720
00:33:59,690 --> 00:34:01,760
but I know because of your complaint,

721
00:34:01,790 --> 00:34:04,200
the shampoo incident was exposed.

722
00:34:04,310 --> 00:34:06,650
And I've never told anyone else about it.

723
00:34:11,770 --> 00:34:13,030
I'm really sorry about today.

724
00:34:13,030 --> 00:34:14,800
Due to the mistake we made in our work,

725
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:16,570
you have to change to another room.

726
00:34:16,570 --> 00:34:18,830
Thank you for cooperating with our work.

727
00:34:20,199 --> 00:34:20,920
Which room?

728
00:34:22,570 --> 00:34:23,790
1825.

729
00:34:25,179 --> 00:34:27,659
It's the one on the edge.

730
00:34:27,870 --> 00:34:29,010
That's an east-facing room,

731
00:34:29,010 --> 00:34:30,320
but it's without afternoon heat
from the setting sun.

732
00:34:30,320 --> 00:34:31,580
It's a prime location.

733
00:34:33,150 --> 00:34:35,090
Why don't you work as a saleswoman
in a real estate company?

734
00:34:35,090 --> 00:34:36,449
Prime location, huh?

735
00:34:38,190 --> 00:34:40,000
I'll bring the room card for you later

736
00:34:40,000 --> 00:34:41,530
along with a fruit platter.

737
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:43,070
Once that gentleman moves out,

738
00:34:43,070 --> 00:34:44,880
we'll immediately arrange for you to move

739
00:34:44,880 --> 00:34:46,409
back to your previous room.

740
00:34:53,020 --> 00:34:54,060
Please come in.

741
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:02,000
I didn't expect the shampoo incident

742
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:03,060
would involve you.

743
00:35:03,210 --> 00:35:04,730
But luckily, you can keep your job now.

744
00:35:04,730 --> 00:35:05,990
We are even now, right?

745
00:35:15,270 --> 00:35:18,110
Ke, what exactly happened just now?

746
00:35:18,110 --> 00:35:19,780
Miyu, I'm sorry.

747
00:35:19,810 --> 00:35:20,620
That Black Card Ji...

748
00:35:20,620 --> 00:35:21,250
No...

749
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:24,280
When Mr. Ji asked me
to handle the extension of his stay,

750
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:26,000
I was busy with something else.

751
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:28,260
Then I forgot to enter it into the system.

752
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:30,550
How could you
forget such an important thing?

753
00:35:30,550 --> 00:35:32,670
Fortunately,
Mr. Ji took a step back just now.

754
00:35:32,670 --> 00:35:34,430
Otherwise,
what if the guest complained about us?

755
00:35:34,430 --> 00:35:36,710
Miyu, could you keep it a secret for me?

756
00:35:36,710 --> 00:35:38,550
Please. I promise
I won't make this mistake again.

757
00:35:38,550 --> 00:35:39,190
Please.

758
00:35:39,190 --> 00:35:40,320
Alright. Forget it.

759
00:35:40,390 --> 00:35:42,710
This matter ends here
as far as I'm concerned.

760
00:35:42,710 --> 00:35:44,030
But I have to warn you.

761
00:35:44,030 --> 00:35:45,070
You must never

762
00:35:45,070 --> 00:35:46,030
make such a mistake again.

763
00:35:46,030 --> 00:35:47,240
Thank you, Miyu.

764
00:35:47,280 --> 00:35:48,480
I promise
I'll never make this mistake again.

765
00:35:48,480 --> 00:35:49,550
You are truly an angel.

766
00:35:49,550 --> 00:35:50,360
Thank you.

767
00:35:58,850 --> 00:36:00,710
I've heard the famous Black Card Ji

768
00:36:00,710 --> 00:36:03,960
stood up for a female attendant
on the executive floor.

769
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:07,360
You even heard of that?

770
00:36:08,400 --> 00:36:09,760
It looks like
Purong Hotel's biggest problem

771
00:36:09,760 --> 00:36:10,960
is being too gossipy.

772
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:13,110
I've never made any gossip.

773
00:36:13,110 --> 00:36:14,960
I'm just a porter of gossip.

774
00:36:15,820 --> 00:36:16,960
Why couldn't I sense that

775
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:19,220
you would show such kindness to a rookie?

776
00:36:19,510 --> 00:36:22,070
The HSKP Department
was reselling daily necessities,

777
00:36:22,070 --> 00:36:23,920
which involved an attendant.

778
00:36:23,920 --> 00:36:26,000
I was already investigating this clue,

779
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:28,400
so I just helped her out.

780
00:36:29,070 --> 00:36:30,710
You just helped her out?

781
00:36:31,150 --> 00:36:34,030
Then you just
helped with her promotion to forewoman?

782
00:36:34,030 --> 00:36:36,110
I wasn't so capable...

783
00:36:38,150 --> 00:36:39,550
as to help an attendant who got

784
00:36:39,550 --> 00:36:41,760
all three bad reviews
in just one month of working here

785
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:43,760
to promote to forewoman overnight.

786
00:36:44,070 --> 00:36:45,760
Is Purong's current promotion system

787
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:46,960
really this chaotic?

788
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:49,710
You're easily surprised
as you haven't seen much.

789
00:36:49,710 --> 00:36:51,000
This is nothing.

790
00:36:51,070 --> 00:36:53,550
At Purong Hotel,
that's just a piece of cake.

791
00:36:54,190 --> 00:36:55,960
Go take a look inside the hotel.

792
00:36:56,320 --> 00:36:58,110
There are stories
of confusing right and wrong.

793
00:36:58,110 --> 00:36:59,360
Their dramatic plots

794
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:01,690
are completely beyond your imagination.

795
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:02,760
In my opinion,

796
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:04,090
what happened to Xu Miyu

797
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:06,060
was at least not a farce.

798
00:37:06,230 --> 00:37:07,760
That's already quite good.

799
00:37:08,480 --> 00:37:09,590
Do you know Xu Miyu?

800
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:13,930
I guess I'm the one
who discovered her talent.

801
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:16,410
Were you the one who recruited her?

802
00:37:18,070 --> 00:37:19,590
I think she's pretty good.

803
00:37:20,710 --> 00:37:22,840
She's both beautiful and smart.

804
00:37:23,400 --> 00:37:24,590
It's just a pity that

805
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:27,400
associating with these girls
in the HSKP Department

806
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:28,710
is a bit of a waste of her talent

807
00:37:28,710 --> 00:37:30,230
and is holding her back.

808
00:37:30,630 --> 00:37:31,510
Ji Feng.

809
00:37:32,150 --> 00:37:33,360
If you're really determined

810
00:37:33,360 --> 00:37:35,400
to reorganize Purong Hotel,

811
00:37:35,400 --> 00:37:37,880
you must have your own people by your side
who you can trust

812
00:37:37,880 --> 00:37:39,360
and are also capable.

813
00:37:39,960 --> 00:37:42,110
Xu Miyu is a very suitable candidate.

814
00:37:43,550 --> 00:37:45,010
You think she's suitable?

815
00:37:47,150 --> 00:37:49,280
I think she's too weak in personality.

816
00:37:49,630 --> 00:37:51,850
She won't remain in the position
of forewoman for long.

817
00:37:51,850 --> 00:37:55,010
If I ask someone whose position
is precarious to be my trusted aide,

818
00:37:55,010 --> 00:37:56,270
what's the use of that?

819
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:00,690
I think it's quite good.

820
00:38:23,570 --> 00:38:27,210
[REC]

821
00:38:37,550 --> 00:38:38,840
What happened?

822
00:38:39,550 --> 00:38:40,750
It hurts, doesn't it?

823
00:38:41,510 --> 00:38:42,400
It hurts, huh?

824
00:39:00,400 --> 00:39:01,570
Ke Wenxue, Ke Wenxue.

825
00:39:01,570 --> 00:39:03,300
Are you in charge of Corridor A?

826
00:39:03,710 --> 00:39:04,590
No, I'm not.

827
00:39:04,590 --> 00:39:05,710
I swapped with someone else.

828
00:39:05,710 --> 00:39:06,910
Who did you swap with?

829
00:39:07,550 --> 00:39:08,840
I also forgot.

830
00:39:09,590 --> 00:39:11,630
Why didn't you guys
follow the shift schedule?

831
00:39:11,630 --> 00:39:14,360
Things would get messed up easily
if you swap by yourselves like this.

832
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:16,030
It's messy not because of me.

833
00:39:16,030 --> 00:39:17,000
As soon as Luo Qingping took a leave,

834
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:18,860
everyone's shifts got messed up.

835
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:21,590
Alright. I got it.

836
00:39:26,920 --> 00:39:28,360
Is anyone there?

837
00:39:28,360 --> 00:39:30,510
Someone in our room
is having an allergic reaction.

838
00:39:30,510 --> 00:39:32,510
Her neck is all swollen.

839
00:39:32,510 --> 00:39:33,510
Coming!

840
00:39:34,310 --> 00:39:35,310
What's wrong?

841
00:39:39,070 --> 00:39:40,070
Hurry up!

842
00:39:42,070 --> 00:39:42,960
Right here.

843
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:44,630
It's so severe.

844
00:39:44,630 --> 00:39:45,840
I'll contact the receptionists

845
00:39:45,840 --> 00:39:47,360
and ask them
to bring some allergy medicine up here.

846
00:39:47,360 --> 00:39:48,110
Please wait a moment.

847
00:39:48,110 --> 00:39:48,960
Go at once.

848
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:49,880
Hurry up.

849
00:39:51,230 --> 00:39:53,670
Today, it just feels so itchy.

850
00:39:54,030 --> 00:39:54,630
As a result...

851
00:39:54,630 --> 00:39:55,550
It's alright, Fang.

852
00:39:55,550 --> 00:39:56,400
It's alright.

853
00:39:56,960 --> 00:39:58,960
We've prepared so hard
for over half a year,

854
00:39:58,960 --> 00:40:01,960
but we didn't even make it
to the finals in the end.

855
00:40:02,070 --> 00:40:03,550
This is really...

856
00:40:06,150 --> 00:40:07,150
I'm sorry.

857
00:40:07,150 --> 00:40:08,590
The Front Office is really so busy.

858
00:40:08,590 --> 00:40:09,880
I'll go downstairs to get it right now

859
00:40:09,880 --> 00:40:10,800
and bring it up here immediately.

860
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:11,710
Please wait a moment.

861
00:40:11,710 --> 00:40:13,030
Okay.

862
00:40:13,030 --> 00:40:13,590
Please hurry up.

863
00:40:13,590 --> 00:40:16,190
-Bring it here as soon as possible.
-Thank you.

864
00:40:16,780 --> 00:40:18,100
Don't cry.

865
00:40:20,070 --> 00:40:21,070
What is this for?

866
00:40:21,400 --> 00:40:22,030
In the past few days,

867
00:40:22,030 --> 00:40:23,400
her neck problem has relapsed.

868
00:40:23,400 --> 00:40:24,590
She can't sleep on a pillow,

869
00:40:24,590 --> 00:40:25,710
so she can only put a towel

870
00:40:25,710 --> 00:40:27,200
under her neck and sleep on it.

871
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:27,920
In the past few days,

872
00:40:27,920 --> 00:40:30,400
Fang has really suffered a lot.

873
00:40:43,550 --> 00:40:44,400
Yin Xiang.

874
00:40:46,280 --> 00:40:48,150
We have an important guest
coming tomorrow.

875
00:40:48,150 --> 00:40:49,070
The room is already booked.

876
00:40:49,070 --> 00:40:50,070
It's Room 1818.

877
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:51,860
Go clean it now.

878
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:54,400
Miyu, why are you only telling me now?

879
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:56,520
My shift is almost over.

880
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:59,800
Don't you still have half an hour
before your shift ends?

881
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:00,710
Half an hour.

882
00:41:01,030 --> 00:41:02,550
Just wait another half an hour.

883
00:41:02,550 --> 00:41:04,140
And then ask someone else to clean it.

884
00:41:04,140 --> 00:41:05,270
I'm leaving now.

885
00:41:09,280 --> 00:41:13,280
The guest in Room 1817 is complaining
about allergies caused by towels.

886
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:14,450
I'll be right there.

887
00:41:16,800 --> 00:41:18,480
Why is it getting worse?

888
00:41:18,710 --> 00:41:20,800
Do you need me to contact the hospital?

889
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:23,360
We're going to
the high-speed rail station soon.

890
00:41:23,360 --> 00:41:25,840
She can go to the hospital
after she gets home.

891
00:41:25,840 --> 00:41:28,490
But the towel issue
must be resolved first.

892
00:41:28,800 --> 00:41:29,510
You have to

893
00:41:29,510 --> 00:41:31,030
give us an explanation today.

894
00:41:31,030 --> 00:41:31,880
Yes.

895
00:41:31,880 --> 00:41:34,340
We can't leave
until this issue is resolved.

896
00:41:34,550 --> 00:41:35,550
Allergies to towels?

897
00:41:35,550 --> 00:41:36,800
Absolutely.

898
00:41:37,000 --> 00:41:40,000
Such a situation
has never happened to her before.

899
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:41,360
But just in the past few days,

900
00:41:41,360 --> 00:41:43,150
after putting this towel from your hotel

901
00:41:43,150 --> 00:41:44,840
under her neck to sleep on it,

902
00:41:44,840 --> 00:41:45,710
she has gotten this allergic reaction.

903
00:41:45,710 --> 00:41:47,070
I'll go report this situation

904
00:41:47,070 --> 00:41:48,230
to our superiors right now.

905
00:41:48,230 --> 00:41:49,470
Please wait a moment.

906
00:41:49,840 --> 00:41:51,020
Okay. Please hurry up.

907
00:41:51,020 --> 00:41:52,050
We have a train to catch.

908
00:41:51,900 --> 00:41:54,190
[REC]

909
00:41:52,190 --> 00:41:53,510
Okay. I'll be right back.

910
00:41:53,510 --> 00:41:54,800
Please hurry up.

911
00:41:55,320 --> 00:41:57,400
This hotel is not okay.

912
00:41:57,480 --> 00:41:59,150
If it's really because of the towel,

913
00:41:59,150 --> 00:42:00,920
we need to ask them for compensation.

